data.description: BRING ON SUMMER FUN in this fantastic 5 bedroom pool home in a very desirable Green Valley neighborhood. If you need space, this is it! With 3,316 sf, this spacious home has all you're looking for. The unrivaled outdoor space features a Pebble tech heated pool & spa with a rock waterfall, slide, and a covered patio. Downstairs, you'll find a two-story formal living room, adjacent dining room, expansive family room with gas fireplace and a junior bedroom suite with its own bath - perfect for generational living! The dramatic dual staircase delivers you upstairs to 4 LARGE bedrooms AND a bonus room with french doors & built-ins. The primary suite has dual vanities, a makeup counter, separate jetted tub, shower & walk-in closet. All new stainless appliances, 3 car garage with workbench, brand new HVAC, pool pump, newer water heater & water softener. Too much to list! Conveniently located near shopping, dining, entertainment, and freeway access.
